Document: AudioEffectEQ
Path: godot/classes/class_audioeffecteq.rst
Summary: AudioEffectEQ methods for managing equalizer band count and gain adjustments.

Method: get_band_count() → int
Returns the number of bands of the equalizer.

Method: get_band_gain_db(int band_idx) → float
Returns the band's gain at the specified index, in dB.

Method: set_band_gain_db(int band_idx, float volume_db)
Sets band's gain at the specified index, in dB.